						<summary>

						<p>On the Dambe pillar in the Vaidyanātha temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">1626 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the setting up of Dambe [Stone pillar] in the temple of Vaidyanatha Swamy. Who caused its not known.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 1548, Kshaya, Jeshṭha, Śu. 1. It corresponds to 1626 A.D., May 16, Tuesday.</p>						

